snippet: Mitt Romney's narrow victory in Iowa looks ugly on the stat sheet, but it accomplished quite a bit when you consider the broader context.
abstract: Mitt Romney's narrow victory in Iowa looks ugly on the stat sheet, but it accomplished quite a bit when you consider the broader context.
lead_paragraph: I don't care if you call it a win or a tie. In Iowa on Tuesday, Mitt Romney had a performance that looks ugly on the stat sheet, but which accomplished quite a bit when you consider it in its broader context.

headline.main: Romney's Ugly Win May Be a Charm
